import { library } from "@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core";

import {
  faHome,
  faFileInvoiceDollar,
  faFileInvoice,
  faFileUpload,
  faFileDownload,
  faSignOutAlt,
  faFolderPlus,
  faBars,
  faCalculator,
  faTimes,
  faCogs,
  faCashRegister,
  faSearch,
  faTrashAlt,
  faEdit,
  faArrowLeft,
  faArrowRight,
  faPlus,
  faMinus,
  faTimesCircle,
  faUserPlus,
  faCoins,
  faShoppingBasket,
  faInfoCircle,
} from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";

library.add(
  faHome,
  faFileInvoiceDollar,
  faFileInvoice,
  faFileUpload,
  faFileDownload,
  faSignOutAlt,
  faFolderPlus,
  faBars,
  faCalculator,
  faTimes,
  faCogs,
  faSearch,
  faCashRegister,
  faTrashAlt,
  faEdit,
  faArrowLeft,
  faArrowRight,
  faArrowRight,
  faPlus,
  faMinus,
  faTimesCircle,
  faUserPlus,
  faCoins,
  faShoppingBasket,
  faInfoCircle
);
